  <zone type="main">
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">Alas!</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough">reflection in</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough">the</del>
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">my</add>
      </mod> present situation was</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">impossible</del><add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">one in
        which all</add><add><ptr target="#c57-0157.01"/></add> – I was hurried away by fury –
      Revenge alone</line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">inspired</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">endowed</add>
      </mod> me with strength, <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">&amp; power of action</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">&amp; composure</add>
      </mod> – It</line>
    <line>modelled my feelings <add place="superlinear">&amp;</add> allowed me to be
      calculating</line>
    <line>and calm <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">when otherwise</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">at periods when otherwise</add>
      </mod> delirium or death</line>
    <line>would have been my portion. My first resolution was</line>
    <line>to quit Geneva for ever.– My country which when</line>
    <line>I was happy &amp; beloved was dear me <mod type="additions">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">now in my adversity</add>
      </mod> became hateful</line>
    <line>I provided myself with a small sum of money</line>
    <line><add><ptr target="#c57-0157.02"/></add> a few jewels <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">that</del>
        <add resp="#pbs" place="superlinear">which</add>
      </mod> had belonged to my mother</line>
    <line>&amp; <del rend="strikethrough">left it</del>. departed</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line>And now my wanderings began which are to</line>
    <line>cease but with life – I have traversed a vast</line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="smear">extent</del>
        <add resp="#pbs" place="superlinear">portion</add>
      </mod> of <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">country</del>
        <add resp="#pbs" place="superlinear">the earth</add>
      </mod> and <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">have</add> endured all the hardships</line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="smear">that</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">which</add>
      </mod> travellers in desarts &amp; barbarous countries</line>
    <line>are wont to meet – How I <mod type="additions">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">have</add>
      </mod> lived I hardly know</line>
    <line><del rend="smear">for</del> many times <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">did</del>
        <add place="superlinear">have</add>
      </mod> I <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">lie</del>
        <add place="sublinear" resp="#pbs"><del rend="smear"><unclear reason="overwritten"/></del>
          stretched my failing limbs</add>
      </mod> on the sandy plain</line>
    <line>exhausted &amp; far from succour, &amp; prayed for</line>
    <line>death – But revenge kept me alive – I dared</line>
    <line>not die &amp; leave my adversary in being.—</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line>When I quitted Geneva my first <del rend="double-strike"><unclear precision="low"
          reason="illegible" unit="chars" extent="1"/></del> labour</line>
    <line>was to gain some <mod type="additions">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">clue</add>
      </mod> by which I might trace</line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">his</del>
        <add place="superlinear">the</add>
      </mod> steps <mod type="additions">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">of my fiendish enemy</add>
      </mod>. But my plan was unsettled and I</line>
    <line>wandered many hours around the confines</line>
    <line>of <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">Geneva</del>
        <add place="superlinear">the town</add>
      </mod> uncertain what path <mod>
        <del rend="smear">to</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">I should</add>
      </mod> pursue</line>
    <line>As night approached I found myself at the</line>
    <line>entrance of the cemetary, where William, Eliza</line>
    <line>beth and my father reposed – I entered it &amp;</line>
    <line>approached the <del rend="strikethrough">toom</del> tomb which marked their</line>
    <line>graves. Every thing was silent except the</line>
    <line>leaves of the trees which <add place="superlinear">were</add> gently <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">rustled</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">agitated</add>
      </mod> by the</line>
    <line>breeze — The night was nearly dark and the</line>
    <line>scene would have been even to an unin</line>
    <line>terested observer affecting and solemn–the</line>
    <line>spirits of the <mod>
        <del rend="double-strike">d</del>
        <add place="superlinear">departed</add>
      </mod> seemed to flit around and <mod type="additions">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">to cast</add>
      </mod> a</line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">gentle</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough">hallow</del>
        <add><ptr target="#c57-0157.03"/></add>
      </mod> around <add place="superlinear">the</add> head of the mourner. <del rend="smear"
        >But</del></line>
  </zone>
